---
title: Message Sent
layout: base.njk
description: "Thank you for getting in touch. I will get back to you shortly."
---

<style>
  .success-section {
    padding: 3rem 1rem;
    min-height: 80vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .success-card {
    background: #1a202c;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #2d3748;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    max-width: 500px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .success-icon {
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: #4FD1C5;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .success-card h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .success-card p {
    color: #a0aec0;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .back-home-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background: #4FD1C5;
    color: #111;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
  }

  .back-home-btn:hover {
    background: #3dbcb2;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
</style>

<section class="success-section">
  <div class="success-card">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check success-icon"></i>
    <h1>Message Sent!</h1>
    <p>Thank you for reaching out. I've received your message and will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
    <a href="/" class="back-home-btn">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Home
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
